chapters.title: These names are synonymous with 90's glam. Their faces evoke memories of glamorous runways and magazine covers.
But did you know they were also the faces of an unlikely venture for supermodels?
The brainchild of Italian brothers and entrepreneurs Tommaso and Francesco Buti
the first location open in the famed Rockefeller Center in NYC in the spring of 1995.
Check out our channel for the full story.
